---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About - Anu Photography"
  description="Learn about Anu, a passionate photographer specializing in landscapes, portraits, and artistic photography."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative py-32 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-heading font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">
        About Anu
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        A passionate photographer dedicated to capturing the beauty of the world through landscapes, 
        intimate portraits, and creative artistic expressions.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16 items-center">
        <!-- Photo -->
        <div class="mb-12 lg:mb-0">
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="aspect-[3/4] overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-2xl">
              <img 
                src="/images/optimized/artsy/IMG_0536-Edit.jpg" 
                alt="Anu - Professional Photographer" 
                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                loading="eager"
              />
            </div>
            <!-- Decorative element -->
            <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 w-32 h-32 bg-gray-900 rounded-full opacity-10"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
              Behind the Camera
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              <p>
                Welcome to my world of photography. I'm Anu, and I've been passionate about 
                capturing moments and emotions through my lens for over a decade. What started 
                as a hobby has evolved into a deep artistic pursuit that drives me to explore 
                new perspectives every day.
              </p>
              <p>
                My photography journey spans across diverse subjects - from the raw beauty of 
                natural landscapes to the intimate expressions in portrait sessions, and the 
                creative experiments that push the boundaries of traditional photography.
              </p>
              <p>
                Every image tells a story, and my goal is to create photographs that not only 
                document moments but evoke emotions and preserve memories that will be 
                treasured for generations to come.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">
              My Approach
            </h3>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
              <p>
                <strong class="text-gray-800">Landscapes:</strong> Patience and timing are everything. 
                I chase the perfect light and wait for nature to reveal its most stunning moments.
              </p>
              <p>
                <strong class="text-gray-800">Portraits:</strong> Connection is key. I work to make 
                my subjects comfortable, capturing genuine expressions and authentic personalities.
              </p>
              <p>
                <strong class="text-gray-800">Artistic:</strong> Experimentation and creativity drive 
                this work, pushing beyond conventional boundaries to create unique visual narratives.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services and Contact CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-900 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-heading font-bold mb-6">
        Let's Create Something Beautiful Together
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-90">
        Whether you're looking for professional portraits, need coverage for a special event, 
        or want to commission custom artistic work, I'd love to discuss your vision.
      </p>
      <div class="space-x-4">
        <a 
          href="/contact" 
          class="inline-block bg-white text-gray-900 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors duration-300"
        >
          Get In Touch
        </a>
        <a 
          href="/galleries/landscapes" 
          class="inline-block border-2 border-white text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-white hover:text-gray-900 transition-all duration-300"
        >
          View My Work
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>